    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/about/?69.html">快捷导航</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?68_1.html">潍博资讯</a></div>
      <span>潍博资讯</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">潍博首届文创产品大赛完美落幕</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%;">&nbsp;<span style="line-height: 35px; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">为进一步推进潍博的文创产品研发，打造出具有潍坊区域特色、在国内外有影响力的文创品牌，潍博紧紧围绕</span><span style="line-height: 35px; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">“</span><span style="line-height: 35px; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">潍坊元素、文物元素、潍坊市博物馆元素</span><span style="line-height: 35px; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">”</span><span style="line-height: 35px; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">三大核心要素，举办了</span><span style="line-height: 35px; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">“</span><span style="line-height: 35px; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">首届潍坊市文化创意产品设计</span><span style="line-height: 35px; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">”</span><span style="line-height: 35px; text-indent: 37px; font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 19px;">大赛，并通过微信公共服务号、云平台、网站等新媒体，加强了对大赛的宣传力度，吸引了众多文创团队、艺术设计者、文物爱好者的踊跃参加，在潍坊文创界掀起了一次文创热潮。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px; line-height: 35px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312">大赛从</span>4月份开始，截止到7月10日，共收到来自学校、社会、个人提供的参赛作品300余件，最终经过大众评选、专家评审等多个筛选环节，其中55件参赛作品以其符合原创性、实用性、艺术性等标准入围。其中，名著红丝石书系列、一品文官补子真丝缎面丝巾、吃亏是福红木嵌银筷子、毛公鼎包装设计、陶瓷笔洗礼盒等作品，因以潍博馆藏藏品为设计元素，以潍坊悠久的历史文化为核心，设计风格新颖独特，获得了大众评审和专家评委的一致青睐。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px; line-height: 35px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312">潍博将以此大赛为契机，今年力争新研发出</span></span><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 19px">10—20</span><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312">种具有潍坊地域特色及潍博馆藏文物鲜明特征的代表性文创产品，进一步打响潍坊文创产品的招牌。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px; text-align: left; line-height: 35px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; text-align: center; line-height: 35px;"><img src="/upload/image/20161229/14830241101193326.jpg" title="1.jpg" alt="1.jpg"/><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 35px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 16px">《名著红丝石书系列》作者：今蔚堂</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 35px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 16px"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 56px; line-height: 35px; text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/image/20161229/14830241174629026.jpg" title="2.jpg" alt="2.jpg"/><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 103px; line-height: 35px; text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 103px; line-height: 35px; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 16px">《一品文官补子真丝缎面丝巾》作者：李静</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 35px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: 35px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 35px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 16px">《吃亏是福红木嵌银筷子》作者：谭东芳</span></strong><img src="/upload/image/20161229/14830241322356778.jpg" title="3.jpg" alt="3.jpg"/></p><p style="line-height: 35px;"><br/></p><p style="line-height: 35px; text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/image/20161229/14830241385477445.jpg" title="4.jpg" alt="4.jpg"/><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 32px; text-align: center; line-height: 35px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 16px">《陶瓷笔洗》作者：设影人视觉</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 37px; text-align: left; line-height: 35px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 19px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; text-align: center; line-height: 35px;"><img src="/upload/image/20161229/14830241453451429.jpg" title="5.jpg" alt="5.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; text-align: center; line-height: 35px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 楷体_GB2312;font-size: 16px">《毛公鼎包装》作者：今蔚</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=166"></script></div>
      
